## 8. Within-Section Sort Order

Within each cross-section group, capabilities are sorted by dimension order first, then by capability order within that dimension. This produces a stable, predictable layout consistent across all respondents.

```sql
ORDER BY gm_dimensions.dimension_order ASC, gm_capabilities.capability_order ASC
```

These values are pulled from `gm_dimensions.dimension_order` and `gm_capabilities.capability_order` via join. No additional rank field is needed for within-section ordering.

